ygData.messageBody:
Many thanks for your concern all =) good to see a
group of ppl without ill will toward each other.

But, I find, in Life we are not always provided with
what we want, more often it is what we need. So,
yesterday I got 2 new jobs to replace the one lost.
One, at the Pancake Palace, and the other at Arby's,
and though with this setup of jobs, sleep will be a
rare commodity, I'll still try to make time for EQ...
Besides who needs more than 3 hours of sleep in any
given day anyway?

Thanks for the support, guys PsyKo
